data.description: Beautiful 3 Bedroom, 2 Bath home with Office on a Large, Corner Lot in Briarwood West! Property Features: Living Room with Gas Fireplace, Remodeled Kitchen, Formal Living and Dining Area, Breakfast Room, Separate Utility Room, Office, 2 Guest Rooms with Spacious Guest Bath, Master Suite, 10x12 Storage Shed, Sprinkler System & More! Remodeled Kitchen with Granite Counters, Subway Tile Backsplash, Double Ovens, Gas Stove. Master Suite with Remodeled Attached Bath with Walk In Shower. 10x12 Storage Building, Large Private Backyard with Great Patio. New Fence, New Flooring & More. Well Cared For Home in Fantastic Location! A Must See!
